==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Breakage
<hw>Break"age</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
act of breaking; a break; a breaking; also, articles broken.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An allowance or compensation for things broken
accidentally, as in transportation or use.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Breakaway</ent>⟦br⟧
